==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} Polluc-, Pollux Pollux + English -ite (after German pollux pollucite)

===Noun===
'''pollucite'''
# {{mineralogy}} A colorless [[transparent]] [[mineral]] of the [[zeolite]] family consisting of [[hydrous cesium aluminum silicate]] and occurring [[massive]] or [[crystallizing]] in [[cube]]s.

